Best practices for making plots:
	
	Problem:										Solution:
	1. Data are meaningless							Do good science
	2. Smoothing is misleasding						Be judicious w/ smoothing (or have theory to explain)
	3. Observations not stated (n=?)				State observations or show them
	4. Plot exists									Show simple data w/ table or text
	5. Visual complexity							Simplify
	6. Poor resolution								Save plots at display size